# Cline Rules for GetIcon

# Changelog Rules
- When making changes to the project, update CHANGELOG.md
- Add new entries under the [Unreleased] section
- Use appropriate subsections: Added, Changed, Deprecated, Removed, Fixed, Security
- When bumping version in Cargo.toml, create a new version section in CHANGELOG.md
- Include the release date in YYYY-MM-DD format

# README Rules
- Keep README.md in sync with project features and functionality
- Update API documentation when endpoints change
- Update installation instructions when build process changes
- Update environment variables section when new variables are added
- Update features list when new features are implemented
- Ensure Docker instructions remain accurate
